data.description: Bishop's Landing is a coastal-inspired community featuring new single-family and villas in Millville. Embrace low-maintenance living, with proximity to Bethany Beach and Route 1 a few minutes away. 10,000 sq. ft. clubhouse and two tennis courts. Quick drive to Rehoboth and Ocean City. Second floor loft options for select plans. Pond view homesites available.
